text: Awesome property on shy 2 acres! You'll love the privacy this home provides. 2 bed/1.75 bath in home with an amazing Detached (42'x48' SF) Shop with Kitchenette and 3/4 bath. Office in home could be used as a 3rd Bedroom (non conforming). Great Room concept with Kitchen open to Living space and vaulted gives you spaciousness for entertaining and relaxing. Lots of windows bringing the outdoors inside. New deck surrounds 2 sides. Metal Roof on both buildings. Attached 2 car garage + shop/garage parking gives you up to 6 car parking on site! Never worry about power here with a 24kW generator on site. You'll love living on this peaceful property! Welcome Home!

Nice rambler style Duplex in Burlington! Each unit boasts 3 bedrooms, 1 3/4 bath, 1080 sq ft of living space, kitchen with all appliances including stack washer and dryer, covered front patio, fenced backyard and a one car garage. Located on a dead end street, close to shopping, restaurants, I5 and more!

Welcome home to this beautifully remodeled craftsman home. Enjoy simple living on an easy to maintain lot and home. Walking distance to many downtown amenities. This home has 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths. Luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout the home and wall to wall carpet in the upstairs bedrooms. Stainless steel appliances and quartz countertops. High efficient heat pump and AC perfect for the cold winters and hot summers. Backyard has two sheds and room for entertaining. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity.

This recently remodeled charmer on a fully fenced lot is sure to suit all your needs. With New carpet, interior paint, plumbing fixtures, light fixtures and appliances, this home is move-in-ready. There is plenty of space with 4 total bedrooms and a bonus room for office, entertainment, whatever your heart desires! Located in a lovely neighborhood with community parks and proximity to the college as well as shopping, restaurants, and bus line. Don't hesitate or it will be gone!

Welcome to Alpine Fairway Villa! Charming one level Condo in Eaglemont offering open floor plan, living room & open vaulted ceiling, large dining room w/ slider to patio to truly enjoy manicured yard w/ privacy and nature. Large kitchen w/ like new stainless-steel appliances & quartz counters and open to cozy family room w/ fireplace. Spacious owner suite w/walk-in shower, jetted tub, separate dressing area with plenty of closets. Laundry room leads to garage with shelving & workshop area. Newer furnace & Air conditioner. Sq.footage per Assessor, builder said 1500 + sq.ft Buyer to verify!! HOA dues include building insurance, landscape maintenance & exterior painting & roof.

Youll want to live in this stunning 3262sqft home on a beautifully treed, shy 5 acres. The main house boasts a spacious primary suite, opulent walk-in closet & lux 5pc en-suite. Theres so much room in the living room & dont miss the work space w/ 220v-is it a commercial kitchen, gym space or craft/studio you decide! Remodeled 2124sqft ADU: 3 bds, 2 ba, bonus storage theater? Wine cellar? Ideal set up for guests. So many outdoor amenities: 220v, chicken coop, playsets, dog kennel, multiple spigots, a stunning iron gazebo & water fountain ready for you to transform it into the perfect oasis or event venue. The possibilities are endless with this one of a kind gem!

Nestled on 9.83 acres of rare flat farm land, this Cape Cod style home with picturesque landscape exudes the charm of the 1940s era while offering modern comforts. Upon stepping inside you'll find hardwood floors & exposed beams that add character to the interior, while large windows flood the space with natural light, creating an inviting and airy feel. The remodeled kitchen has newer appliances nestled amidst plenty of cabinetry for storage offering both functionality and appeal. The living areas are cozy yet spacious, perfect for hosting gatherings or unwinding by the wood fireplace. Whether you're savoring a meal on the porch or simply taking in the sights and sounds this of rural life, this home offers a timeless retreat

Welcome to this beautifully updated home nestled in a serene country setting, just minutes away from downtown Mount Vernon. Open floor plan with large windows to allow a lot of natural light. Newly renovated kitchen, modern cabinets and brand new stainless steel appliances with detached coffee bar. This single-level home with a basement has 3 bedrooms, 2.25 bathrooms and office space offers plenty versatile living and storage space, office could be used as another bedroom! Updates galore! New roof in 2023, fresh exterior paint, new flooring, and a fresh coat of interior paint. Partially fenced, with a cozy fire pit, perfect for gatherings with friends. Lots of gardening space as well! This home is truly a must-see.

This perfect home away from home is waiting for you! Enjoy the peaceful lake located in the foothills of the North Cascade Mountains with a serene view of Mount Baker. This community offers a plethora of fun, including 2 heated swimming pools, 2 hot tubs, a large clubhouse with games & entertainment provided, covered grills, picnic benches, beach volleyball, boat launch, kayak storage, multiple playgrounds, 18 hole mini golf, disk golf, tennis court, horseshoe pits, dog runs & more! This place really has it all whether you are looking to go fishing, paddle boarding, kayaking, swimming or just sit by a fire and enjoy the great outdoors. This lot offers an adorable trailer with 296 sq ft room addition plus a shed & comfort station close by!

Immerse yourself in the serene beauty of waterfront property, boasting a double-sided dock framing majestic vistas of Mt. Baker, the Cascades, & the iconic Rainbow Bridge, all visible from your waterfront home. Entertain guests on the expansive patio, offering the perfect backdrop for every occasion. Inside, relish in the luxury of Italian marble-adorned kitchen, and an inviting island for gathering. Feel the warmth of radiant heat flooring throughout, even extending to the spacious two-car garage. Every corner of this remarkable abode offers panoramic views, promising a lifestyle of unparalleled serenity in addition to the Shelter Bay amenities.

Nestled within the serene & sought-after Twin Brooks 55+ community, this beautiful single level home is a testament to elegant living amidst landscaped beauty. This lovely home boasts an open & airy floor plan, designed with comfort & accessibility in mind. Each room is bathed in natural light, highlighting the exquisite details and craftsmanship that define the interior. The living room, with its cozy gas fireplace and custom shelving, offers a warm invitation to relax & unwind. The modern kitchen features top-of-the-line appliances, ample counter space w/island & timeless cabinetry that provides plenty of storage while the adjacent dining area is perfect for enjoying your morning coffee while gazing out at the tranquil backyard.

Welcome to this spacious four bedroom, two full bath home on a large fenced lot. Open Kitchen offers all new appliances, and garbage disposal, with dining room, den/office, and large living room providing open living. Vaulted ceilings in living room, lighten up this oversized room. Master bathroom has a full bath and walk-in closet and additional 3 good sized bedrooms. Two car garage offers lots of storage including loft style storage. Lots of space in the fenced back yard with patio. Home is conveniently close to shopping, schools and I5 for convenient commuting.

Fantastic Opportunity! Excellent 4 plex zoned Commercial Business District in the heart of Anacortes. The building is situated in the middle of a large 10, 492 SF lot with ample onsite parking, street parking, and alley. Just one block off Commercial Ave affords a nice walk to numerous restaurants, shopping, waterfront, and many other amenities that the very desirable Anacortes community is so sought after for. The building while in its original condition is in good shape given the caring long term tenants. Two 2beds 1bath and, two 1bed 1 bath. All feature nice kitchens w/dishwashers, dining, ample living rooms, and individual laundry. New roof installed. Please do not disturb the tenants.
nearby_schools: Northwest Educational Service District 189, Anacortes School District

text: Embrace the tranquil allure of water and island views from this captivating abode! Situated on a spacious corner lot, this home boasts Pergo laminate flooring, complemented by a custom kitchen featuring maple cabinets & granite countertops. Feel the warmth of the living room, complete with a remote-controlled gas fireplace adorned with faux marble tile surround. Recent upgrades include a 30-year roof & window & doors replacements. Enjoy privacy & ambiance with custom top-down/bottom-up blinds. Outdoors, the cedar fence encloses a double gate, perfect for RV parking on the RV pad, equipped with a 50 amp power connection. Beautiful landscaping accentuated by a newly painted deck & railings. Welcome home to luxury & functionality intertwined!

Cozy & Unique custom-built home in beautiful Anacortes! Top quality throughout w/ bamboo & tile floors, granite countertops, Mahogony custom trim, unique windows, gas fireplace, radiant heat & tankless hot water. Kitchen has eating bar, nook for table, walk-in pantry & SS appliances. Guest bedroom, full bath & laundry room on main. Upper floor has huge primary bedroom, gorgeous bath with tile doorless shower, soaking tub and large vanity with storage. Separate room off primary can be used for office, exercise or nursery. This room has French doors out to a covered deck. 24x24 detached garage w/power, water, heat & bathroom. Beautiful covered front porch! So many wonderful features, & close to quaint downtown & ferry! You must see this gem!

This beautifully remodeled home has 4-bed, 2-bath home boasting 1546 sq ft of single-story living. The open-concept kitchen dazzles with extra cabinets, Quartz countertops, a spacious island, walk-in pantry, and stainless steel appliances. Entertain effortlessly on the large patio deck overlooking the expansive, fully fenced backyard complete with a cozy fire pit. Plus, enjoy the convenience of RV parking and additional side parking. Perfectly situated near schools, shopping centers, hospitals, and with easy access to I-5, this home offers both style and convenience in one unbeatable package.
